    ( <i>Carla humming</i> )           

00:09.700 --> 00:11.900
        Boy, look at her.       

00:11.900 --> 00:12.900
            What a glow she has.

00:12.900 --> 00:14.300
            You know, strange   
            as it sounds,       

00:14.400 --> 00:15.500
                  there are     
                  actually times

00:15.500 --> 00:16.700
                when I resent   
                being a man.    

00:16.700 --> 00:18.000
Ah, that's all right, Fras.     

00:18.000 --> 00:19.600
Sometimes <i>we</i> resent             
you being one.                  

00:19.700 --> 00:21.300
                  ( <i>Sam laughs</i> )

00:22.600 --> 00:24.600
              I was referring to
              Carla's condition.

00:24.600 --> 00:25.800
             You see, she's able

00:25.800 --> 00:28.100
to do something                 
we men never shall--            

00:28.100 --> 00:29.900
         experience the miracle 
         of creating a new life.

00:30.000 --> 00:31.400
                  SAM:          
                  You know, I'll
                  have to admit.

00:31.400 --> 00:33.000
I've often wondered             
what it would like              

00:33.000 --> 00:35.400
to have another human being     
moving around inside you.       

00:35.500 --> 00:37.500
                 Must be spooky,
                 but real neato.

00:37.500 --> 00:38.900
    Yeah.                       

00:39.000 --> 00:41.100
There's probably nothing        
so awesome                      

00:41.200 --> 00:42.700
in the entire universe.         

00:42.800 --> 00:44.100
                 Yes, gentlemen,
                 I'm afraid     

00:44.100 --> 00:45.300
                  that we've    
                  been relegated

00:45.400 --> 00:46.800
                 to the position
                 of observer.   

00:46.800 --> 00:49.300
            Passive, sitting    
            on the sidelines.   

00:49.400 --> 00:52.000
              Doomed by nature  
              to a life of envy.

00:52.000 --> 00:54.300
        God, feels like         
      there's a dump truck      

00:54.400 --> 00:56.400
     parked on my bladder.      

00:57.600 --> 00:59.100
            Well, then again,   

00:59.100 --> 01:01.800
                  nature is wise
                  in her way.   

